Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.26,0:28:48.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.51,0:28:53.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你还能够说是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.47,0:28:58.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}崩坏的砂器散落一地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:04.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}破碎的心能否重新拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.10,0:29:13.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何人的呼唤 幻化为耳鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.24,0:29:18.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}时间似乎静止
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:21.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}啊 觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.24,0:29:26.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}冲破这无边的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.42,0:29:31.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}疾风一般逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.65,0:29:36.27,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}曾如行尸走肉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.27,0:29:43.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们 到城墙之外 再相见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:47.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在地图之外
